### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@contentType = application/json

### Get all clients
GET {{baseUrl}}/clients

### Get client by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/clients/CLI-001

### Create new client
POST {{baseUrl}}/clients
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "id": "CLI-001",
  "name": "Juan Pérez",
  "phone": "+58 412-1234567",
  "address": "Av. Principal, Caracas"
}

### Update client
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/clients/CLI-001
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Juan Pérez Actualizado",
  "phone": "+58 412-7654321",
  "address": "Nueva dirección, Caracas"
}

### Delete client
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/clients/CLI-001
